  <brief_title>Cortical Visual Impairment and Visual Attentiveness</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cortical Visual Impairment and Visual Attentiveness: The Effect of Visual and Cross-Modal Environments on Children Diagnosed With Cerebral Palsy and Cortical Visual Impairment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
